                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": true,
                    "title": "Description"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "Like CyDown, but for everything except Cydia. Erika can download paid tweaks for free in Installer 5, Saily, Sileo, and Zebra."
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false,
                    "title": "Features"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "- Identical tweak database to CyDown \n- Pretty UI with progress bar buttons \n- Supports all modern package managers \n- Open source"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false,
                    "title": "Instructions"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "1. In *Saily*, tap the Buy button then Erika. In *everything else*, tap the tweak's icon at the top of the depiction. \n2. Once the tweak has downloaded, tap on Get Zappy. \n3. If you don't have Filza with URL scheme, the deb files are found in /var/mobile/Media/Erika."
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false,
                    "title": "Known Issues"
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "- Does not work in Xina! I don't have Xina so if you can figure out why it's not working, hmu. \n- 'Tweak not found on the server' is not a bug, it just means CyDown server doesn't yet have the tweak."
                },
                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSeparatorView"
                },
                
